host_about:
Hi! My name is Katrin and I am happy to welcome you to my little home!
Usually I am sharing it with two little tigers and up to two flat mates, but whenever one of us is abroad for a longer period of time I am happy to open my doors and host you! 
if you just stay here for a weekend or a longer period, whatever you prefer -  communication, cooking, discussions in our kitchen or just informations - we´re sure to tell you the only, the correct solution :)
